<item>
            <title>[MNG-729] Ability to additional ArtifactHandlers using external components.xml</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MNG-729</link>
                <project id="12316922" key="MNG">Maven (Moved to GitHub Issues)</project>
                    <description>
&lt;p&gt;I have a need to add a new ArtifactHandler using my own components.xml. It turns out the the setting is ignored unless I &lt;br/&gt;
merge my xml to maven-artifact/src/main/resources/META-INF/plexus/components.xml and bootstrap m2 to take affect.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Here is an example of my components declaration&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &amp;lt;component&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;role&amp;gt;org.apache.maven.artifact.handler.ArtifactHandler&amp;lt;/role&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;role-hint&amp;gt;native&amp;lt;/role-hint&amp;gt; &lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;implementation&amp;gt;org.apache.maven.artifact.handler.DefaultArtifactHandler&amp;lt;/implementation&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;configuration&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
           &amp;lt;type&amp;gt;dll&amp;lt;/type&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
           &amp;lt;extension&amp;gt;dll&amp;lt;/extension&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
           &amp;lt;packaging&amp;gt;native&amp;lt;/packaging&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
       &amp;lt;/configuration&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &amp;lt;/component&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
