                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="14420285" author="kenney" created="Fri, 12 Aug 2005 18:51:56 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This component isn&apos;t added to the HandlerManager&apos;s list of available Handlers,&lt;br/&gt;
because it uses a List&lt;img class=&quot;emoticon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/emoticons/help_16.png&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt; to store the Handlers. The component should already be discovered before&lt;br/&gt;
the HandlerManager is configured (looked-up), to be added to that list.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;A modification of the HandlerManager to look up components for unknown role-hints etc.&lt;br/&gt;
could be made. It was done for the CompilerManager too.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Comments?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14408475" author="brettporter" created="Fri, 12 Aug 2005 19:03:20 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Kenney - this alrready works when &amp;lt;extensions&amp;gt; is added to the pom using the plugin, but according to dan this isn&apos;t working.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14420319" author="dantran" created="Sun, 21 Aug 2005 08:07:38 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;based on comments, not sure if this issue is fixed&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14408598" author="brettporter" created="Sun, 21 Aug 2005 08:46:03 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;it wasn&apos;t, but I fixed it and closed it. it works now (continuum is our working example)&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
